What is creational design pattern?
 Creational deign pattern deals with creation of object.

1. Singleton design pattern
Ensure that class has only one instance and provides a global point of access to that instance.

Working of singleton pattern
1. Private constructor: Prevents instantiation from outside the class
2. Static variable: Hold the single instance of the class
3. Public static method: Provides a global access point to the instance

Approaches to implement singleton pattern:
1. Eager loading: When the class is loaded instance also created
2. Lazy loading: When the requirement comes then only instace is created.
